Bootstrap can be used in a React application to quickly design responsive UI.

1ï¸âƒ£ Install Required Libraries

Run the following command in the project terminal:

npm i bootstrap bootstrap-icons


âœ” Installs Bootstrap CSS, JS, and Icons inside node_modules

2ï¸âƒ£ Link Bootstrap Files in main.jsx

Add the following imports at the top of main.jsx:

